data.description: Welcome to 759 East 218th Street in the Williamsbridge section of the North-Central Bronx! Inside this detached multilevel, multiunit  two Family home. On the top floor, the 2 bedroom unit features a walk-out terrace off one of the bedrooms facing the front of the home. The 1st floor 3 bedroom unit is spread between 2 floors and has 1 1/2 baths. There is a 1 car driveway and some outdoor space as well. The property is located feet from the Bronx River Pkwy and steps away form the 2 train line! This is a great location for commuters who drive or take public transit! This gem is a great opportunity for investment income! It''s already equipped with 2 furnaces and 2 water heaters! Do!Not!Miss!Out!
